  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use four-dimensional thinking to control time and navigate through the world of <strong>Beta MAX</strong>. This atmospheric first-person puzzle platformer takes you on a journey with Max, who has been thrust into a retro-futuristic 80's inspired world full of increasingly complex puzzles.<br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216250/extras/c1e76bf62efc37faa678505387850719.poster.avif?t=1750529802\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216250/extras/c1e76bf62efc37faa678505387850719.webm?t=1750529802\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216250/extras/c1e76bf62efc37faa678505387850719.mp4?t=1750529802\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>You Will</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Pause and rewind time </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Manoeuvre objects onto floor switches and remotely activate wall switches </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Utilise time chambers and velocity accelerators </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Dodge lasers and avoid crushers </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Travel on moving platforms and traverse fragmenting bridges </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216250/extras/3a4092edc4275513356e2946ccd31d2c.poster.avif?t=1750529802\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216250/extras/3a4092edc4275513356e2946ccd31d2c.webm?t=1750529802\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216250/extras/3a4092edc4275513356e2946ccd31d2c.mp4?t=1750529802\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>On Each Level</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Find the hidden collectible </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Overcome all obstacles to complete without errors </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Move with speed and precision to get under par-time</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216250/extras/f67abd0785cb3f17ab7389ab205dad28.poster.avif?t=1750529802\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216250/extras/f67abd0785cb3f17ab7389ab205dad28.webm?t=1750529802\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216250/extras/f67abd0785cb3f17ab7389ab205dad28.mp4?t=1750529802\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use four-dimensional thinking to control time and navigate through the world of <strong>Beta MAX</strong>. This atmospheric first-person puzzle platformer takes you on a journey with Max, who has been thrust into a retro-futuristic 80's inspired world full of increasingly complex puzzles.<br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216250/extras/c1e76bf62efc37faa678505387850719.poster.avif?t=1750529802\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216250/extras/c1e76bf62efc37faa678505387850719.webm?t=1750529802\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216250/extras/c1e76bf62efc37faa678505387850719.mp4?t=1750529802\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>You Will</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Pause and rewind time </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Manoeuvre objects onto floor switches and remotely activate wall switches </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Utilise time chambers and velocity accelerators </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Dodge lasers and avoid crushers </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Travel on moving platforms and traverse fragmenting bridges </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216250/extras/3a4092edc4275513356e2946ccd31d2c.poster.avif?t=1750529802\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216250/extras/3a4092edc4275513356e2946ccd31d2c.webm?t=1750529802\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216250/extras/3a4092edc4275513356e2946ccd31d2c.mp4?t=1750529802\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>On Each Level</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Find the hidden collectible </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Overcome all obstacles to complete without errors </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Move with speed and precision to get under par-time</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216250/extras/f67abd0785cb3f17ab7389ab205dad28.poster.avif?t=1750529802\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216250/extras/f67abd0785cb3f17ab7389ab205dad28.webm?t=1750529802\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216250/extras/f67abd0785cb3f17ab7389ab205dad28.mp4?t=1750529802\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
